**TEASER:**

This modern retelling of “The Tempest” in Palm Springs captures the essence of Shakespeare’s themes of betrayal, love, and redemption, while also commenting on the fleeting nature of fame in the entertainment industry.

*Setting:* In the luxurious desert oasis of Palm Springs, A modern McMansion with a pool and hot tub area that are the envy of everyone who doesn’t have one. Instead of an island, the story unfolds around a grand, secluded clothing optional hotel in the heart of Palm Springs, surrounded by vast desert landscapes.

